name: Wewe Putih
shortLoreBlurb: Wewe Putih is a spirit from Java/Indonesia linked to white ghost, night. Mediates with the dead and fate.
overlapsLinks: Anubis (Egyptian), Chandra (Hindu), Chang'e (China), Hel (Norse), Tsukuyomi (Japan), Yama (Buddhist)
